{"tid":2104464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"致仲諗緊投唔投嘅本土派 初選對激進派絕對係利多於弊","createTime":"2020-07-12T03:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T08:05:07.000Z","uid":225100,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1beb88d74a819736c078f46ee549a8264651cc4e","tid":2104464,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T03:46:59.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">endorse 功能組別?</span><br />\n如果你同我一樣預計本土派9成會DQ<br />\n你就唔會當今次超區係一次普通嘅功能組別選舉<br />\n而係一個<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\">本土派點人數</span></span>嘅機會<br />\n睇下本土派由4年前嘅17%去到今日係有幾多%<br />\n因為 正選根本冇得投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">endorse 泛民?</span><br />\n一步踢走晒所有泛民係妄想 亦不切實際<br />\n但只踢走老電池嘅話係絕對可能<br />\n5區本土派就算只有16年嘅17%票<br />\n由於激進派投票意欲比溫和派高<br />\n而溫和派嘅票亦會比新晉年輕泛民吸納<br />\n最終激進本土入閘嘅機會絕對係高嘅<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">除非 你杯葛</span> <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">驚泛民反口?</span><br />\n到時就係佢哋分化啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最鍾意屌分化撚<br />\n有時唔好真係當選民白痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">信唔過戴妖區軒?</span><br />\n老戴坐完監係變咗 區軒自己都有監未坐<br />\n信任呢樣野真係冇得講 你要堅信佢哋會做馬<br />\n冇人改變到你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span class=\"red\">投黎有撚用咩我9月係唔係都投本土架啦</span></blockquote><br />\n國安法後第一次點人數<br />\n歐美實mon實<br />\n9月可能DQ晒冇本土你投<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"blue\"><span class=\"xx-large\">今日9am至9pm<br />\n<strong>主席 <br />\n本土派要求點人數</strong><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b848ccd2fc33168169e031c266744978073475b9","tid":2104464,"uid":225100,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T03:49:33.000Z","msg":"經一眾連登仔訓話後最新名單<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n港島：<span class=\"red\">梁晃維</span> <del>彭卓棋</del> 袁嘉蔚<br />\n九西：<span class=\"red\">馮達浚</span> 劉澤鋒 張崑陽<br />\n九東：<span class=\"red\">李嘉達</span> 黃之鋒<br />\n新西：<span class=\"red\">張可森</span> <span class=\"gold\">伍健偉</span> 黃子悅<br />\n新東：<span class=\"red\">鄒家成</span> <span class=\"gold\">劉頴匡</span> 呂智恆 <del>何桂藍</del><br />\n超區：<span class=\"red\">王百羽</span> 岑敖暉<br />\n<br />\n新東新西絕對夠票兩席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b88696e2967216be36976da106c3696e95ad0980","tid":2104464,"uid":225100,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T03:53:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WfPxWsc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWfPxWsc.jpg&h=0d76fcc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">讓本土成為主流</span>"},{"pid":"c30db45b951d9284cb688fb9ed3be9b384f7e7ae","tid":2104464,"uid":99391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T04:00:04.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49efb1f2efa2907a6a04df00612f0e156e2ddd64","tid":2104464,"uid":99391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T04:00:15.000Z","msg":"本土要人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e305ab94a6554cb5d85b1332621de75329a721d","tid":2104464,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T04:00:17.000Z","msg":"初選教學 [附逐頁截圖]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2103342\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2103342</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b9268